   Which of the following may result in a crash at runtime if the user presses Enter without typing a response?
   
   Option A) ::
   
      yesno = input('Enter Yes or No:')
      if yesno[0] == 'Y' and len(yesno) > 0:
         print('Yes!')
   
   Option B) ::
   
      yesno = input('Enter Yes or No:')
      if len(yesno) > 0 and yesno[0] == 'Y':
         print('Yes!')